## Educational and Research Use Notice

This software is designed for educational and research purposes only. It is a
simulation environment that does not execute real exploit code. All activities are
contained within isolated Docker environments.

Users are responsible for:
- Ensuring compliance with local laws and regulations
- Using the software only for authorized security research
- Not using the software for malicious purposes
- Properly securing any deployed instances

The authors assume no liability for misuse or unauthorized use of this software.
